        "descriptions": [
          {
            "descriptionType": "Abstract",
            "description": "The file Radiosondage.pdf shows two atmospheric soundings in Ajaccio (Corsica) and Cuneo (Italy), on November 2nd, 2022, at 00:00 UTC. The file minute20.png shows the LMA VHF sources vertical distribution within the storm producing the luminous event, during 10 minutes between 20:15 and 20:25 UTC on November 2, 2022. The following files (minute 30.png etc..) shows the same distribution for 10 minutes and 10 minutes later."
          }
